WEBVTT

00:01:35.720 --> 00:01:41.040 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:01:41.150 --> 00:01:43.740 line:80%
[Episode 16]

00:01:43.850 --> 00:01:47.150 line:80%
[Yixiang Restaurant]

00:01:45.309 --> 00:01:47.640 line:80%
You are Manager Yu of Yixiang Restaurant?

00:01:47.870 --> 00:01:48.510 line:80%
That's me.

00:01:49.010 --> 00:01:49.750 line:80%
Take her away.

00:01:49.750 --> 00:01:50.440 line:80%
Yes!

00:01:52.440 --> 00:01:53.080 line:80%
Alright.

00:01:53.520 --> 00:01:55.980 line:80%
I'll go to the magistrate's office
with you.

00:02:11.600 --> 00:02:12.360 line:80%
It's me.

00:02:14.360 --> 00:02:15.640 line:80%
By order of the Magistrate,

00:02:15.640 --> 00:02:17.600 line:80%
Yixiang Restaurant shall remain sealed

00:02:17.600 --> 00:02:19.460 line:80%
until the murder case is solved.

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:21.830 line:80%
To prevent destruction of evidence,

00:02:22.120 --> 00:02:23.390 line:80%
guard this building strictly!

00:02:23.390 --> 00:02:24.110 line:80%
Yes!

00:02:27.850 --> 00:02:28.990 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:02:28.990 --> 00:02:29.950 line:80%
You were gone for a long time,

00:02:29.950 --> 00:02:31.280 line:80%
so I came to check on you.

00:02:31.820 --> 00:02:32.650 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:02:33.110 --> 00:02:34.800 line:80%
It's Qianqian who's in trouble.

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:36.040 line:80%
I plan to kidnap that bastard magistrate

00:02:36.040 --> 00:02:37.030 line:80%
and get Qianqian out.

00:02:37.030 --> 00:02:38.390 line:80%
You take Changning and hide.

00:02:38.390 --> 00:02:39.360 line:80%
If I get caught,

00:02:39.879 --> 00:02:41.080 line:80%
take good care of her.

00:02:41.080 --> 00:02:42.270 line:80%
Who came up with this stupid idea for you?

00:02:42.270 --> 00:02:43.110 line:80%
I did.

00:02:45.110 --> 00:02:46.480 line:80%
I'm just speaking hypothetically.

00:02:46.480 --> 00:02:47.160 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:02:47.160 --> 00:02:49.490 line:80%
I'll strike when the magistrate is alone.

00:02:49.550 --> 00:02:50.610 line:80%
I won't get caught.

00:02:51.990 --> 00:02:54.110 line:80%
Kidnapping the magistrate is useless.

00:02:54.110 --> 00:02:55.370 line:80%
Someone with ulterior motives
is using the grain requisition

00:02:55.370 --> 00:02:56.830 line:80%
to incite the villagers to cause trouble.

00:02:56.830 --> 00:02:58.800 line:80%
Yixiang Restaurant is just a beginning.

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:01.880 line:80%
They're deliberately provoking the people
to rebel against the government

00:03:01.880 --> 00:03:04.510 line:80%
so that the Jizhou Government Troops
will come and suppress them,

00:03:04.510 --> 00:03:05.760 line:80%
proving the rumor

00:03:05.780 --> 00:03:09.200 line:80%
that the Court's grain requisition
has forced the people into rebellion.

00:03:09.200 --> 00:03:11.130 line:80%
How do you know this?

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:14.230 line:80%
I'll tell you later.

00:03:15.040 --> 00:03:17.110 line:80%
Go find Constable Wang now

00:03:17.129 --> 00:03:19.270 line:80%
and tell him to take his men
to guard the city gates.

00:03:19.270 --> 00:03:21.330 line:80%
Do not let the rioters enter the city.

00:03:22.230 --> 00:03:22.670 line:80%
Wait.

00:03:23.550 --> 00:03:25.110 line:80%
If the rioters enter the city,

00:03:25.110 --> 00:03:27.390 line:80%
they'll only go after
the magistrate and the police runner.

00:03:27.390 --> 00:03:29.510 line:80%
Why should I stop them for those people?

00:03:29.510 --> 00:03:31.710 line:80%
These people have been pushed
to the brink.

00:03:31.710 --> 00:03:33.430 line:80%
You really think they only want justice?

00:03:33.430 --> 00:03:34.600 line:80%
Once they get into the city,

00:03:34.600 --> 00:03:35.600 line:80%
they won't let

00:03:35.620 --> 00:03:37.520 line:80%
any of the wealthy and powerful go.

00:03:37.520 --> 00:03:38.520 line:80%
One step further,

00:03:38.780 --> 00:03:41.710 line:80%
and they could turn into rebels
looting and burning.

00:03:43.700 --> 00:03:46.629 line:80%
What if the authorities
refuse to release the grain?

00:03:49.140 --> 00:03:50.670 line:80%
Contain the rioters first.

00:03:50.670 --> 00:03:52.070 line:80%
I'll figure out the rest.

00:03:52.870 --> 00:03:53.400 line:80%
Okay.

00:03:54.480 --> 00:03:55.600 line:80%
When I go find Constable Wang,

00:03:55.600 --> 00:03:57.000 line:80%
I'll take Bao'er with me.

00:03:57.170 --> 00:03:57.740 line:80%
No.

00:03:58.510 --> 00:03:59.760 line:80%
I have another way

00:03:59.780 --> 00:04:01.310 line:80%
to ensure Bao'er's safety.

00:04:11.240 --> 00:04:13.070 line:80%
If you can't control the mob,

00:04:15.050 --> 00:04:16.579 line:80%
you must protect yourself.

00:04:25.070 --> 00:04:25.720 line:80%
I'm going.

00:04:40.400 --> 00:04:40.990 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:04:40.990 --> 00:04:42.190 line:80%
What are you holding?

00:04:43.670 --> 00:04:44.310 line:80%
I'm talking to you!

00:04:44.310 --> 00:04:44.959 line:80%
Stop!

00:04:45.630 --> 00:04:46.400 line:80%
That kid!

00:04:46.870 --> 00:04:47.630 line:80%
You stay here and keep watch.

00:04:47.630 --> 00:04:48.160 line:80%
Yes!

00:04:49.600 --> 00:04:50.400 line:80%
Come, Bao'er.

00:04:54.480 --> 00:04:56.070 line:80%
Yixiang Restaurant is safe now.

00:04:56.070 --> 00:04:57.300 line:80%
Hide in the dark room.

00:04:57.430 --> 00:04:59.110 line:80%
No matter who calls you,
don't make a sound.

00:04:59.110 --> 00:05:00.400 line:80%
I see, Auntie Changyu.

00:05:00.750 --> 00:05:02.800 line:80%
You must get my mother out.

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:05.400 line:80%
Don't worry. I will.

00:05:05.420 --> 00:05:06.050 line:80%
Go on.

00:05:10.880 --> 00:05:13.390 line:80%
[Qingping County Government Office]

00:05:13.420 --> 00:05:16.250 line:80%
[Government]

00:05:19.280 --> 00:05:20.920 line:80%
Has the scout sent any news?

00:05:21.840 --> 00:05:23.700 line:80%
Has Wei Xuan arrived with his men?

00:05:24.520 --> 00:05:26.530 line:80%
There is no news yet.

00:05:29.850 --> 00:05:31.280 line:80%
First, transport the grain seized

00:05:31.280 --> 00:05:33.280 line:80%
from the merchants and commoners

00:05:33.280 --> 00:05:34.930 line:80%
of Qingping County out of here.

00:05:34.930 --> 00:05:41.500 line:80%
[Sui Yuanqing,
Heir Apparent of Lord Changxin]

00:05:35.190 --> 00:05:36.630 line:80%
Our 1000 troops

00:05:36.630 --> 00:05:38.160 line:80%
are still waiting outside.

00:05:39.280 --> 00:05:41.480 line:80%
If that idiot Wei doesn't show up,

00:05:42.070 --> 00:05:44.530 line:80%
we'll kill some of the rioters
for him first.

00:05:50.870 --> 00:05:53.430 line:80%
But these rioters
want to join us in Chongzhou.

00:05:53.430 --> 00:05:55.520 line:80%
Why do you still want to kill them?

00:05:57.920 --> 00:05:59.250 line:80%
No need to kill them all.

00:05:59.400 --> 00:06:00.600 line:80%
It's just for show.

00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:02.630 line:80%
It's to make the people

00:06:02.630 --> 00:06:04.960 line:80%
completely disappointed with the court.

00:06:06.210 --> 00:06:08.490 line:80%
If we don't cut off their retreat,

00:06:08.720 --> 00:06:11.120 line:80%
they won't sincerely join us in Chongzhou.

00:06:13.850 --> 00:06:16.710 line:80%
Have you caught that brat
from Yixiang Restaurant?

00:06:17.170 --> 00:06:18.600 line:80%
Someone saved him.

00:06:18.600 --> 00:06:20.430 line:80%
But I have already sent men
to pursue them.

00:06:20.430 --> 00:06:22.480 line:80%
News will come back soon.

00:06:24.430 --> 00:06:25.870 line:80%
Don't hurt the child.

00:06:26.290 --> 00:06:28.110 line:80%
After all,
he is my older brother's flesh and blood.

00:06:28.110 --> 00:06:28.750 line:80%
Yes.

00:06:31.950 --> 00:06:34.310 line:80%
What about the woman in the prison?

00:06:34.310 --> 00:06:37.250 line:80%
Regarding how to deal
with my brother's concubine,

00:06:37.400 --> 00:06:39.630 line:80%
we'll take her back
and let my brother decide for himself.

00:06:39.630 --> 00:06:41.720 line:80%
Just make sure no one humiliates her.

00:06:44.870 --> 00:06:45.480 line:80%
Yes.

00:06:53.630 --> 00:06:54.720 line:80%
My Lady.

00:06:54.920 --> 00:06:55.990 line:80%
I haven't seen you for a long time,

00:06:55.990 --> 00:06:57.750 line:80%
and you still look so healthy.

00:06:58.400 --> 00:06:59.520 line:80%
Our Yan

00:06:59.520 --> 00:07:01.840 line:80%
is about to go to the capital
for the imperial exam.

00:07:01.840 --> 00:07:04.190 line:80%
He misses you very much.

00:07:04.280 --> 00:07:06.600 line:80%
So he had me buy some trinkets

00:07:06.630 --> 00:07:08.630 line:80%
and give them to you personally.

00:07:12.600 --> 00:07:13.310 line:80%
Lu.

00:07:13.920 --> 00:07:14.600 line:80%
Yes.

00:07:15.280 --> 00:07:16.600 line:80%
Scholar Song is very thoughtful.

00:07:16.600 --> 00:07:17.800 line:80%
You're too kind.

00:07:18.280 --> 00:07:19.110 line:80%
Is there anything else?

00:07:19.110 --> 00:07:20.750 line:80%
A few days ago, your mother

00:07:20.750 --> 00:07:22.670 line:80%
complimented the pattern on my shoes,

00:07:22.670 --> 00:07:24.640 line:80%
so I specially brought it over today,

00:07:24.640 --> 00:07:26.550 line:80%
thinking I could give it to her

00:07:26.550 --> 00:07:27.670 line:80%
when we have tea.

00:07:29.070 --> 00:07:30.750 line:80%
Mother caught a cold

00:07:30.750 --> 00:07:31.800 line:80%
and hasn't recovered yet.

00:07:31.800 --> 00:07:32.750 line:80%
It's not suitable for her to see visitors.

00:07:32.750 --> 00:07:35.040 line:80%
I'll thank you on her behalf.

00:07:35.480 --> 00:07:37.340 line:80%
Lu, see the guest out.

00:07:37.830 --> 00:07:38.300 line:80%
Yes.

00:07:38.390 --> 00:07:39.959 line:80%
Then I shouldn't disturb her.

00:07:39.959 --> 00:07:42.890 line:80%
-Well, I'll come another day.
-Madam Song, this way.

00:07:52.750 --> 00:07:54.080 line:80%
Who do you think you are,

00:07:54.750 --> 00:07:56.870 line:80%
acting like a highborn lady?

00:07:57.520 --> 00:07:59.430 line:80%
You're just a magistrate's daughter.

00:07:59.430 --> 00:08:00.480 line:80%
Do you really think our Yan

00:08:00.480 --> 00:08:02.340 line:80%
will beg on his knees to marry you?

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:05.700 line:80%
You had the nerve to accept my gift

00:08:06.190 --> 00:08:07.110 line:80%
but didn't even

00:08:07.110 --> 00:08:09.280 line:80%
invite me in for a cup of tea.

00:08:09.650 --> 00:08:11.040 line:80%
What kind of person is that?

00:08:11.040 --> 00:08:11.550 line:80%
Go!

00:08:13.040 --> 00:08:13.960 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:08:16.520 --> 00:08:17.360 line:80%
Get in there!

00:08:17.720 --> 00:08:20.380 line:80%
-What are you waiting for? Get in!
-How dare you!

00:08:20.550 --> 00:08:21.430 line:80%
Don't try to play tricks!

00:08:21.430 --> 00:08:22.280 line:80%
Open the door!

00:09:07.390 --> 00:09:09.250 line:80%
They're all fake police runners.

00:09:09.520 --> 00:09:10.590 line:80%
My Lady.

00:09:11.710 --> 00:09:14.150 line:80%
Why don't you... have some soup?

00:09:14.640 --> 00:09:15.950 line:80%
At a time like this,

00:09:16.030 --> 00:09:17.760 line:80%
you still want me to drink soup?

00:09:20.310 --> 00:09:21.370 line:80%
What's that noise?

00:09:28.590 --> 00:09:29.320 line:80%
Who's there?

00:09:31.550 --> 00:09:32.350 line:80%
You are...

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:34.120 line:80%
Fan Changyu?

00:09:38.040 --> 00:09:39.240 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:09:39.550 --> 00:09:40.950 line:80%
Forget it, I'll just make something up.

00:09:40.950 --> 00:09:42.880 line:80%
Save me the trouble of explaining.

00:09:43.240 --> 00:09:44.570 line:80%
Constable Wang sent me.

00:09:45.810 --> 00:09:49.340 line:80%
He felt that something was wrong
at the county office recently.

00:09:49.470 --> 00:09:50.880 line:80%
Experience really counts.

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:52.490 line:80%
A group of people came a few days ago.

00:09:52.490 --> 00:09:53.890 line:80%
Their leader claims to be

00:09:53.920 --> 00:09:57.690 line:80%
Wei Xuan, the Military Commissioner
of the Northwest.

00:09:57.950 --> 00:09:59.240 line:80%
He kidnapped my father

00:09:59.350 --> 00:10:02.280 line:80%
and forced him
to levy silver and grain in the county.

00:10:02.280 --> 00:10:03.470 line:80%
And Advisor Guo.

00:10:03.530 --> 00:10:06.280 line:80%
He... he actually
turned traitor to save himself.

00:10:06.280 --> 00:10:07.400 line:80%
Him again.

00:10:07.950 --> 00:10:09.550 line:80%
No wonder he's so shameless.

00:10:10.920 --> 00:10:12.160 line:80%
Miss Fan.

00:10:12.260 --> 00:10:14.320 line:80%
I fought with you over Song Yan before

00:10:14.640 --> 00:10:16.000 line:80%
because I was immature.

00:10:16.000 --> 00:10:17.660 line:80%
Please don't take it to heart.

00:10:19.160 --> 00:10:21.240 line:80%
My father is in Wei Xuan's hands now.

00:10:22.520 --> 00:10:23.760 line:80%
I'm begging you.

00:10:24.070 --> 00:10:25.730 line:80%
Please help me save my father.

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:29.910 line:80%
Song Yan...

00:10:32.350 --> 00:10:33.190 line:80%
Song Yan...

00:10:33.520 --> 00:10:34.760 line:80%
I'll let you have Song Yan.

00:10:34.760 --> 00:10:35.430 line:80%
No, no.

00:10:36.920 --> 00:10:38.830 line:80%
You should keep the Song Yan for yourself.

00:10:38.830 --> 00:10:40.400 line:80%
If you really want to thank me,

00:10:40.400 --> 00:10:41.520 line:80%
after it's done,

00:10:41.800 --> 00:10:43.470 line:80%
let Manager Yu
out of the county office jail

00:10:43.470 --> 00:10:44.950 line:80%
No problem. I promise you.

00:10:45.120 --> 00:10:46.350 line:80%
As long as I can save my father,

00:10:46.350 --> 00:10:47.470 line:80%
I'll do anything.

00:10:52.240 --> 00:10:54.190 line:80%
Can you lend me your maid's outfit?

00:10:54.690 --> 00:11:03.060 line:80%
[Qingping]

00:11:04.070 --> 00:11:04.710 line:80%
Go!

00:11:04.710 --> 00:11:05.350 line:80%
Go!

00:11:05.800 --> 00:11:06.640 line:80%
Return our grain!

00:11:06.640 --> 00:11:07.800 line:80%
Keep up!

00:11:09.190 --> 00:11:10.470 line:80%
Keep up!

00:11:10.670 --> 00:11:12.080 line:80%
Make the bastard magistrate
return our grain!

00:11:12.080 --> 00:11:13.880 line:80%
Make the bastard magistrate
return our grain!

00:11:13.880 --> 00:11:14.800 line:80%
Keep up!

00:11:16.010 --> 00:11:17.190 line:80%
Give it back to us!

00:11:24.460 --> 00:11:26.260 line:80%
They're going to storm the city.

00:11:26.590 --> 00:11:27.470 line:80%
Close the city gate!

00:11:27.370 --> 00:11:29.410 line:80%
[Qingping]

00:11:27.830 --> 00:11:29.360 line:80%
Close the city gate! Hurry!

00:11:33.400 --> 00:11:36.160 line:80%
Magistrate Cui hasn't been seen
at the county office for days.

00:11:36.160 --> 00:11:37.990 line:80%
Luckily, Fan Changyu's husband

00:11:38.040 --> 00:11:40.760 line:80%
noticed something was wrong
and prepared defenses in advance.

00:11:40.760 --> 00:11:42.690 line:80%
Otherwise, we'd be in big trouble.

00:11:45.880 --> 00:11:47.260 line:80%
Keep your eyes peeled.

00:11:47.300 --> 00:11:49.040 line:80%
Put on your Jizhou Army uniforms.

00:11:49.040 --> 00:11:50.190 line:80%
Wait for the insider in the city

00:11:50.190 --> 00:11:51.040 line:80%
to open the gate,

00:11:51.040 --> 00:11:52.350 line:80%
receive the Heir Apparent,

00:11:52.350 --> 00:11:53.910 line:80%
and catch them off guard!

00:11:54.070 --> 00:11:54.830 line:80%
Yes!

00:12:03.400 --> 00:12:04.720 line:80%
Let us in!

00:12:05.120 --> 00:12:06.480 line:80%
Let us in!

00:12:06.670 --> 00:12:08.160 line:80%
I want to enter the city!

00:12:09.920 --> 00:12:11.160 line:80%
Let us in!

00:12:10.900 --> 00:12:13.560 line:80%
[Qingping]

00:12:13.170 --> 00:12:14.430 line:80%
Let us enter the city!

00:12:14.430 --> 00:12:17.090 line:80%
We want to go out!
Why did you close the city gate?

00:12:17.550 --> 00:12:18.550 line:80%
Move! Move aside!

00:12:18.920 --> 00:12:20.470 line:80%
Move! Move!

00:12:20.830 --> 00:12:21.430 line:80%
Leave!

00:12:21.430 --> 00:12:22.470 line:80%
Let us out!

00:12:22.470 --> 00:12:24.120 line:80%
Let me out! Let me out!

00:12:24.120 --> 00:12:25.040 line:80%
We want to live!

00:12:25.040 --> 00:12:25.640 line:80%
Let us out!

00:12:25.640 --> 00:12:26.310 line:80%
Say one more word,

00:12:26.310 --> 00:12:28.390 line:80%
and I'll kill you first!
Do you believe me?

00:12:28.390 --> 00:12:29.990 line:80%
Come out and face your death!

00:12:30.610 --> 00:12:31.660 line:80%
[Qingping]

00:12:30.650 --> 00:12:33.450 line:80%
Bastard magistrate,
come out and face your death!

00:12:33.470 --> 00:12:34.390 line:80%
Leave!

00:12:37.040 --> 00:12:37.640 line:80%
General,

00:12:38.000 --> 00:12:39.040 line:80%
the magistrate here

00:12:39.040 --> 00:12:39.880 line:80%
sent a maid

00:12:39.880 --> 00:12:40.880 line:80%
to bring you soup.

00:12:42.830 --> 00:12:43.960 line:80%
Tell her to get lost.

00:12:44.520 --> 00:12:46.460 line:80%
This maid is quite pretty.

00:12:46.710 --> 00:12:48.280 line:80%
The General told her to get lost.

00:12:48.280 --> 00:12:49.410 line:80%
Didn't you hear him?

00:12:49.430 --> 00:12:49.950 line:80%
Yes.

00:12:51.280 --> 00:12:52.040 line:80%
Wait.

00:12:56.070 --> 00:12:58.950 line:80%
Wei Xuan is known
for being cruel and lecherous.

00:12:59.240 --> 00:13:02.170 line:80%
There's no reason for him
to suddenly become chaste.

00:13:03.660 --> 00:13:05.540 line:80%
Alright. Let her in.

00:13:05.920 --> 00:13:06.470 line:80%
Yes.

00:13:18.000 --> 00:13:18.670 line:80%
My Lord.

00:13:31.640 --> 00:13:32.900 line:80%
Please enjoy, My Lord.

00:13:39.470 --> 00:13:41.070 line:80%
So shy and timid.

00:13:41.120 --> 00:13:42.400 line:80%
Just my type.

00:13:43.430 --> 00:13:45.160 line:80%
Put the food over there for now.

00:13:46.040 --> 00:13:46.770 line:80%
Yes, My Lord.

00:13:51.350 --> 00:13:52.520 line:80%
So he is Wei Xuan?

00:13:54.350 --> 00:13:55.070 line:80%
Forget it.

00:13:55.230 --> 00:13:57.890 line:80%
Whether he is or not,
I'll just kidnap him first.

00:14:12.840 --> 00:14:13.810 line:80%
General!

00:14:14.800 --> 00:14:17.250 line:80%
You'd better not fall into my hands
in the future.

00:14:17.250 --> 00:14:19.160 line:80%
Otherwise, I'll skin you alive

00:14:19.190 --> 00:14:21.250 line:80%
and hang your corpse at the city gate!

00:14:26.830 --> 00:14:28.710 line:80%
You'd better hope you have a future.

00:14:28.710 --> 00:14:30.070 line:80%
Don't hurt our General!

00:14:30.300 --> 00:14:31.520 line:80%
I won't hurt him.

00:14:31.950 --> 00:14:33.980 line:80%
As long as you do as I say.

00:14:34.760 --> 00:14:36.430 line:80%
Do as she says.

00:14:38.190 --> 00:14:40.190 line:80%
I will remember you.

00:14:40.800 --> 00:14:42.310 line:80%
Don't remember me.

00:14:42.330 --> 00:14:45.260 line:80%
I'm just following
the County Magistrate's orders.

00:14:45.280 --> 00:14:46.430 line:80%
Release my Master!

00:14:50.300 --> 00:14:52.780 line:80%
Come out, you bastard official!

00:14:53.350 --> 00:14:54.280 line:80%
Come out!

00:14:54.430 --> 00:14:55.830 line:80%
[Cheongpyeong]

00:14:55.070 --> 00:14:57.830 line:80%
Folks, what are you doing?

00:14:58.000 --> 00:14:59.760 line:80%
Don't let a moment of rage make you commit

00:14:59.760 --> 00:15:02.210 line:80%
a crime punishable by the extermination
of your entire clan!

00:15:02.210 --> 00:15:03.470 line:80%
We will return

00:15:04.120 --> 00:15:05.590 line:80%
the grain seeds to you.

00:15:06.520 --> 00:15:08.160 line:80%
Everyone, go home now!

00:15:08.430 --> 00:15:09.670 line:80%
As for this rebellion,

00:15:09.670 --> 00:15:11.930 line:80%
the government won't pursue it further.

00:15:12.280 --> 00:15:13.120 line:80%
Folks!

00:15:13.200 --> 00:15:15.710 line:80%
Don't be fooled
by that magistrate's lackey!

00:15:15.710 --> 00:15:17.120 line:80%
He's tricking us into going home.

00:15:17.120 --> 00:15:18.160 line:80%
What awaits us

00:15:18.280 --> 00:15:20.520 line:80%
is the same fate as Ma Village!

00:15:20.520 --> 00:15:21.880 line:80%
-Yes!
-Yes!

00:15:21.880 --> 00:15:23.240 line:80%
-Yeah!
-Yes!

00:15:23.240 --> 00:15:25.280 line:80%
Folks! Let's charge into the city

00:15:23.910 --> 00:15:27.850 line:80%
[Qingping]

00:15:25.280 --> 00:15:26.760 line:80%
and kill that bastard magistrate!

00:15:26.760 --> 00:15:28.240 line:80%
Kill the bastard magistrate!

00:15:28.240 --> 00:15:30.700 line:80%
Folks,
regarding the tragedy at Ma Village,

00:15:31.040 --> 00:15:32.760 line:80%
the government will
punish those responsible strictly

00:15:32.760 --> 00:15:34.190 line:80%
and provide everyone
with a proper resolution!

00:15:34.190 --> 00:15:35.450 line:80%
Don't come any closer.

00:15:36.160 --> 00:15:37.880 line:80%
Or we'll shoot!

00:15:43.470 --> 00:15:44.470 line:80%
Should we go?

00:15:44.470 --> 00:15:45.830 line:80%
What should we do?

00:15:58.000 --> 00:15:59.770 line:80%
Master, bad news.

00:15:59.800 --> 00:16:01.040 line:80%
The 200,000 piculs of grain

00:16:01.040 --> 00:16:03.640 line:80%
were intercepted on the way back
to Chongzhou.

00:16:03.920 --> 00:16:04.920 line:80%
Who did it?

00:16:04.920 --> 00:16:07.350 line:80%
They say it was a pincer attack
by two groups.

00:16:07.350 --> 00:16:09.470 line:80%
One was Xie Zheng's Blood-Robed Cavalry,

00:16:09.470 --> 00:16:11.240 line:80%
and the other was the Jizhou Army.

00:16:11.240 --> 00:16:12.800 line:80%
Wasn't He Jingyuan imprisoned

00:16:12.800 --> 00:16:14.060 line:80%
by that idiot Wei Xuan?

00:16:15.870 --> 00:16:19.310 line:80%
So Xie Zheng has been colluding
with He Jingyuan all along.

00:16:21.160 --> 00:16:22.690 line:80%
What a matrilocal husband.

00:16:22.950 --> 00:16:24.760 line:80%
What a Marquis of Wu'an.

00:16:25.000 --> 00:16:27.160 line:80%
He Jingyuan is Wei Yan's trusted aide,

00:16:27.350 --> 00:16:29.710 line:80%
and Xie Zheng
is investigating Wei Yan's past.

00:16:29.710 --> 00:16:31.070 line:80%
How could they join forces?

00:16:31.070 --> 00:16:32.040 line:80%
God knows!

00:16:32.640 --> 00:16:33.350 line:80%
Report!

00:16:35.000 --> 00:16:36.710 line:80%
Our men have successfully infiltrated
the rioters.

00:16:36.710 --> 00:16:37.670 line:80%
And 1,000 elite soldiers of Chongzhou

00:16:37.670 --> 00:16:38.950 line:80%
are hiding outside the city,

00:16:38.950 --> 00:16:40.880 line:80%
ready to support Heir Apparent Sui
at any moment.

00:16:40.880 --> 00:16:43.410 line:80%
Master, although the grain
was intercepted,

00:16:43.470 --> 00:16:45.430 line:80%
our plan to sow discord succeeded.

00:16:45.470 --> 00:16:47.870 line:80%
Your painstaking planning wasn't in vain.

00:16:49.190 --> 00:16:51.240 line:80%
The more civilians die,

00:16:51.520 --> 00:16:53.190 line:80%
the greater the Wei faction's crimes.

00:16:53.190 --> 00:16:54.520 line:80%
The Imperial Court
is forcibly requisitioning grain,

00:16:54.520 --> 00:16:56.670 line:80%
driving the whole county to rebellion.

00:16:56.670 --> 00:16:57.800 line:80%
Such a grave crime—

00:16:58.000 --> 00:16:59.190 line:80%
who could bear it?

00:17:01.190 --> 00:17:03.140 line:80%
I presume by now,

00:17:03.909 --> 00:17:05.830 line:80%
my dear brother, Sui Yuanqing,

00:17:06.389 --> 00:17:09.000 line:80%
should have already met his true opponent.

00:17:18.760 --> 00:17:19.960 line:80%
Release the people from the county office,

00:17:19.960 --> 00:17:21.080 line:80%
or I will kill him.

00:17:21.909 --> 00:17:22.830 line:80%
Go ahead.

00:17:23.440 --> 00:17:24.669 line:80%
Kill me.

00:17:24.830 --> 00:17:27.110 line:80%
Listen up! If I die,

00:17:27.200 --> 00:17:29.310 line:80%
everyone in this county office
will die with me!

00:17:29.310 --> 00:17:30.110 line:80%
Yes!

00:17:30.410 --> 00:17:31.210 line:80%
Stop!

00:17:31.800 --> 00:17:32.830 line:80%
I am here.

00:17:33.310 --> 00:17:34.330 line:80%
Don't be impulsive, everyone!

00:17:34.330 --> 00:17:35.480 line:80%
Don't be impulsive!

00:17:35.550 --> 00:17:36.390 line:80%
Don't be impulsive!

00:17:36.390 --> 00:17:38.590 line:80%
Those outside the city are all rioters.

00:17:38.590 --> 00:17:40.850 line:80%
They've come today to massacre the city.

00:17:41.130 --> 00:17:42.280 line:80%
Let me go,

00:17:42.800 --> 00:17:44.200 line:80%
and I'll leave you alive.

00:17:44.360 --> 00:17:45.420 line:80%
Massacre the city?

00:17:50.870 --> 00:17:51.930 line:80%
Massacre the city?

00:17:52.310 --> 00:17:53.720 line:80%
You dare to massacre the city?

00:17:53.720 --> 00:17:54.550 line:80%
Fine.

00:17:54.720 --> 00:17:56.550 line:80%
I'll drag you to the gate tower right now,

00:17:56.550 --> 00:17:58.610 line:80%
and we'll see who will get massacred.

00:18:00.310 --> 00:18:01.840 line:80%
You're quite interesting.

00:18:02.280 --> 00:18:03.830 line:80%
I'll remember you.

00:18:07.440 --> 00:18:09.100 line:80%
You want to remember me again?

00:18:15.040 --> 00:18:16.070 line:80%
Fine.

00:18:16.280 --> 00:18:18.550 line:80%
You'd better remember how you will die.

00:18:19.590 --> 00:18:21.920 line:80%
My men have already freed the magistrate.

00:18:21.960 --> 00:18:23.440 line:80%
You can let me go now.

00:18:26.310 --> 00:18:27.520 line:80%
When have these bastard officials

00:18:27.520 --> 00:18:29.720 line:80%
ever treated us like humans?

00:18:29.910 --> 00:18:30.960 line:80%
Fire the arrows then!

00:18:30.960 --> 00:18:32.200 line:80%
If I get killed,

00:18:32.220 --> 00:18:35.000 line:80%
just don't forget to collect my body!

00:18:35.070 --> 00:18:37.080 line:80%
Come on! Fire! Fire!

00:18:42.910 --> 00:18:44.240 line:80%
Who ordered you to fire?

00:18:45.110 --> 00:18:46.720 line:80%
Gou, are you okay?

00:18:46.720 --> 00:18:47.310 line:80%
Gou!

00:18:47.390 --> 00:18:48.590 line:80%
Wake up, Gou!

00:18:48.980 --> 00:18:49.630 line:80%
Gou!

00:18:50.390 --> 00:18:53.150 line:80%
You bastard officials!
I'll fight you to the death!

00:18:53.150 --> 00:18:54.150 line:80%
Let's fight them to the death!

00:18:54.150 --> 00:18:54.750 line:80%
Charge in!

00:18:54.830 --> 00:18:55.630 line:80%
Fight!

00:18:55.750 --> 00:18:56.770 line:80%
Charge in!

00:18:58.680 --> 00:18:59.860 line:80%
Charge in!

00:19:09.280 --> 00:19:10.480 line:80%
Hold the one

00:19:10.720 --> 00:19:12.650 line:80%
who fired the arrows accountable.

00:19:13.190 --> 00:19:15.920 line:80%
Don't be stirred up
by those with ill intentions.

00:19:16.280 --> 00:19:16.940 line:80%
Who are you?

00:19:17.960 --> 00:19:18.760 line:80%
I work for you.

00:19:23.760 --> 00:19:25.340 line:80%
The magistrate is now under guard.

00:19:25.340 --> 00:19:27.080 line:80%
Those with red ribbons
are fake police runners.

00:19:27.080 --> 00:19:29.080 line:80%
Tell your men to feel free to attack.

00:19:34.680 --> 00:19:36.480 line:80%
Take down these police runners!

00:19:36.480 --> 00:19:37.210 line:80%
Yes!

00:19:50.760 --> 00:19:51.870 line:80%
Report!

00:19:52.280 --> 00:19:53.830 line:80%
The rioters
are gathering outside the city gate.

00:19:53.830 --> 00:19:55.170 line:80%
A few skilled men

00:19:55.280 --> 00:19:56.460 line:80%
have grabbed
the requisitioned military grain

00:19:56.460 --> 00:19:58.130 line:80%
and are transporting it to the city gate,

00:19:58.130 --> 00:20:01.350 line:80%
saying... saying they are going to
return it to all the rioters.

00:20:01.350 --> 00:20:02.750 line:80%
Yan Zheng has succeeded.

00:20:03.440 --> 00:20:06.270 line:80%
Your operators were certainly thorough.

00:20:07.200 --> 00:20:09.910 line:80%
Right now, this man
has become a hot potato.

00:20:10.040 --> 00:20:11.170 line:80%
If I really kill him,

00:20:11.240 --> 00:20:13.240 line:80%
I'd be killing a high-ranking official.

00:20:13.240 --> 00:20:15.000 line:80%
I guess I'll have no choice
but to take Changning with me

00:20:15.000 --> 00:20:16.870 line:80%
to a bandit den
and hide there for the rest of our lives.

00:20:16.870 --> 00:20:18.530 line:80%
But if I let him go,

00:20:18.960 --> 00:20:21.000 line:80%
I won't have an easy life later.

00:20:22.960 --> 00:20:24.070 line:80%
My Lord,

00:20:24.410 --> 00:20:26.130 line:80%
the villagers of Lin'an Town

00:20:26.200 --> 00:20:27.870 line:80%
have rebelled over the grain requisition.

00:20:27.870 --> 00:20:29.480 line:80%
You have to provide them with a resolution

00:20:29.480 --> 00:20:30.610 line:80%
to calm their anger.

00:20:31.480 --> 00:20:32.390 line:80%
Well...

00:20:32.960 --> 00:20:35.440 line:80%
I dare not make a decision on this.

00:20:35.520 --> 00:20:36.680 line:80%
The granary is right there.

00:20:36.680 --> 00:20:37.760 line:80%
Just take it.

00:20:37.760 --> 00:20:39.950 line:80%
I'll pretend I don't know.

00:20:40.070 --> 00:20:40.870 line:80%
Father.

00:20:41.520 --> 00:20:43.850 line:80%
You are the magistrate of this county.

00:20:44.240 --> 00:20:45.370 line:80%
If you act like this,

00:20:45.480 --> 00:20:47.390 line:80%
you're worse than a butcher girl—

00:20:47.480 --> 00:20:48.350 line:80%
no sense of responsibility.

00:20:48.350 --> 00:20:49.150 line:80%
Shut up!

00:20:49.240 --> 00:20:50.720 line:80%
What does a mere girl like you know?

00:20:50.720 --> 00:20:52.000 line:80%
This is how politics works.

00:20:52.000 --> 00:20:53.000 line:80%
Once the rioters enter the city,

00:20:53.000 --> 00:20:54.440 line:80%
they'll surely kill some
corrupt officials.

00:20:54.440 --> 00:20:55.720 line:80%
As the magistrate,

00:20:55.720 --> 00:20:57.040 line:80%
I'd be the first to die.

00:20:57.040 --> 00:20:57.590 line:80%
Stop talking.

00:20:57.590 --> 00:20:58.200 line:80%
You...

00:20:58.910 --> 00:21:00.550 line:80%
This magistrate may hold high office,

00:21:00.550 --> 00:21:02.200 line:80%
but he's timid as a mouse.

00:21:03.070 --> 00:21:05.200 line:80%
I have to take a gamble on his daughter.

00:21:06.480 --> 00:21:09.480 line:80%
My Lady, what should we do
with this bastard official?

00:21:10.040 --> 00:21:10.720 line:80%
Father.

00:21:11.280 --> 00:21:14.150 line:80%
Don't those rioters want a resolution?

00:21:14.280 --> 00:21:16.720 line:80%
You can just push these people out there

00:21:16.960 --> 00:21:19.000 line:80%
and let them answer to the rioters.

00:21:19.590 --> 00:21:20.720 line:80%
That's right.

00:21:21.000 --> 00:21:22.720 line:80%
Pinning the blame on him

00:21:22.960 --> 00:21:24.960 line:80%
makes him the perfect scapegoat.

00:21:26.110 --> 00:21:26.910 line:80%
I understand.

00:21:28.760 --> 00:21:29.760 line:80%
You brought

00:21:29.760 --> 00:21:31.520 line:80%
the grain requisition order,

00:21:31.520 --> 00:21:32.230 line:80%
right?

00:21:32.480 --> 00:21:33.700 line:80%
Now we'll have to trouble you

00:21:33.700 --> 00:21:36.480 line:80%
to go to the city gate

00:21:36.590 --> 00:21:37.800 line:80%
and give the people a resolution.

00:21:37.800 --> 00:21:38.630 line:80%
Very well.

00:21:39.150 --> 00:21:40.800 line:80%
Let's go to the city gate.

00:21:41.680 --> 00:21:43.310 line:80%
I will give you a resolution.

00:21:46.630 --> 00:21:47.000 line:80%
Move.

00:21:47.000 --> 00:21:48.150 line:80%
You guys, take the young lady back.

00:21:48.150 --> 00:21:49.150 line:80%
Father, I'm going too.

00:21:49.150 --> 00:21:49.800 line:80%
Go back.

00:21:56.570 --> 00:21:58.430 line:80%
Keep an eye on those instigators—

00:21:58.550 --> 00:22:00.810 line:80%
they don't act like ordinary villagers.

00:22:05.520 --> 00:22:08.720 line:80%
Come out and face your death!
Come out and face your death!

00:22:09.440 --> 00:22:10.470 line:80%
Folks!

00:22:10.870 --> 00:22:12.720 line:80%
The grain we requisitioned before

00:22:12.720 --> 00:22:14.200 line:80%
will definitely be returned to you.

00:22:14.200 --> 00:22:15.910 line:80%
You are all law-abiding citizens.

00:22:15.910 --> 00:22:17.830 line:80%
Don't let those with ill intentions
lead you

00:22:17.830 --> 00:22:19.240 line:80%
into committing a grave mistake.

00:22:19.240 --> 00:22:21.520 line:80%
For those willing to take the grain
and go home,

00:22:21.520 --> 00:22:23.550 line:80%
we will overlook today's event.

00:22:23.630 --> 00:22:25.630 line:80%
The government
will not pursue this further.

00:22:25.630 --> 00:22:28.290 line:80%
The Jizhou Army is on its way
to Qingping County.

00:22:28.680 --> 00:22:30.760 line:80%
If you break through this city gate today,

00:22:30.760 --> 00:22:32.270 line:80%
there will be no turning back.

00:22:32.270 --> 00:22:33.480 line:80%
For the rest of your lives,

00:22:33.480 --> 00:22:35.680 line:80%
do you want to farm with your families,

00:22:36.150 --> 00:22:38.150 line:80%
or drag your whole family to the grave?

00:22:38.150 --> 00:22:40.090 line:80%
The choice is yours.

00:22:40.440 --> 00:22:41.390 line:80%
Talk is cheap.

00:22:41.410 --> 00:22:42.440 line:80%
Where is the grain?

00:22:42.440 --> 00:22:43.520 line:80%
Yeah, where is the grain?

00:22:43.520 --> 00:22:44.340 line:80%
Where is it?

00:22:44.360 --> 00:22:45.680 line:80%
Where is it?

00:22:46.350 --> 00:22:47.550 line:80%
Where is the grain?

00:22:47.550 --> 00:22:48.760 line:80%
The grain is here!

00:22:54.070 --> 00:22:54.930 line:80%
The grain!

00:22:55.150 --> 00:22:55.800 line:80%
It's the grain!

00:22:55.800 --> 00:22:57.060 line:80%
It really is the grain!

00:22:57.110 --> 00:22:58.520 line:80%
The grain is here!

00:22:58.600 --> 00:22:59.810 line:80%
The grain is here!

00:23:01.680 --> 00:23:02.960 line:80%
Folks!

00:23:03.110 --> 00:23:05.440 line:80%
Your grain is being brought out now!

00:23:09.330 --> 00:23:10.150 line:80%
Hurry! Hurry!

00:23:17.240 --> 00:23:18.280 line:80%
It's the grain!

00:23:18.300 --> 00:23:19.370 line:80%
It really is the grain!

00:23:19.370 --> 00:23:20.480 line:80%
It really is the grain!

00:23:20.480 --> 00:23:21.050 line:80%
Great!

00:23:21.110 --> 00:23:22.150 line:80%
The grain!

00:23:22.390 --> 00:23:23.280 line:80%
We're saved!

00:23:23.280 --> 00:23:24.580 line:80%
We have grain now!

00:23:24.610 --> 00:23:25.690 line:80%
We have grain now!

00:23:28.150 --> 00:23:29.610 line:80%
Miss, may I know your name?

00:23:30.070 --> 00:23:31.870 line:80%
Where shall we meet again?

00:23:32.720 --> 00:23:35.680 line:80%
I don't want to miss out on such a fate.

00:23:35.680 --> 00:23:36.870 line:80%
You're about to die.

00:23:37.200 --> 00:23:38.150 line:80%
Cut the crap.

00:23:39.550 --> 00:23:40.480 line:80%
Constable Wang!

00:23:42.000 --> 00:23:43.260 line:80%
What's the situation?

00:23:44.230 --> 00:23:44.990 line:80%
My Lord!

00:23:51.990 --> 00:23:52.860 line:80%
Yan Zheng?

00:23:52.880 --> 00:23:53.650 line:80%
My Lord,

00:23:53.910 --> 00:23:54.630 line:80%
who's this?

00:23:56.110 --> 00:23:57.590 line:80%
He's a general from Jizhou Prefecture,

00:23:57.590 --> 00:23:59.440 line:80%
here to supervise the grain requisition.

00:23:59.440 --> 00:24:00.510 line:80%
He caused all this,

00:24:00.680 --> 00:24:02.390 line:80%
provoking widespread complaints
among the people.

00:24:02.390 --> 00:24:03.680 line:80%
As your magistrate,

00:24:03.760 --> 00:24:06.020 line:80%
I had no choice but to offend my superiors

00:24:06.130 --> 00:24:07.530 line:80%
and tie up these soldiers

00:24:07.550 --> 00:24:09.690 line:80%
to give the people an explanation.

00:24:09.800 --> 00:24:11.660 line:80%
My Lord, you are truly righteous.

00:24:12.550 --> 00:24:14.720 line:80%
The rioters haven't entered the city yet.

00:24:14.720 --> 00:24:17.850 line:80%
It's all thanks to you
standing guard here with your men.

00:24:17.870 --> 00:24:19.430 line:80%
You didn't let me down.

00:24:19.550 --> 00:24:20.680 line:80%
I am ashamed.

00:24:21.200 --> 00:24:23.350 line:80%
-Actually...
-The bastard officials up there!

00:24:23.350 --> 00:24:24.910 line:80%
The food issue is settled,

00:24:24.930 --> 00:24:27.680 line:80%
but how will you pay for the dozen lives
lost in Ma Village?

00:24:27.680 --> 00:24:29.960 line:80%
With the lives of the bastard magistrate's
whole family?

00:24:29.960 --> 00:24:31.150 line:80%
That's right!

00:24:31.170 --> 00:24:33.570 line:80%
-Pay with your lives!
-Pay with your lives!

00:24:35.070 --> 00:24:36.200 line:80%
You unruly peasant!

00:24:36.390 --> 00:24:38.280 line:80%
How dare you curse a court official!

00:24:38.280 --> 00:24:39.880 line:80%
You all saw that, didn't you?

00:24:40.110 --> 00:24:41.510 line:80%
This bastard magistrate

00:24:41.520 --> 00:24:43.270 line:80%
never saw us as humans,

00:24:43.480 --> 00:24:44.840 line:80%
nor does he have any intention
of giving us an explanation!

00:24:44.840 --> 00:24:46.550 line:80%
If we let them fool us into going back,

00:24:46.550 --> 00:24:48.480 line:80%
we'll just be beaten to death
by these police runners later.

00:24:48.480 --> 00:24:49.280 line:80%
Yeah!

00:24:49.520 --> 00:24:50.350 line:80%
Kill the magistrate!

00:24:50.350 --> 00:24:51.350 line:80%
Kill the magistrate!

00:24:51.350 --> 00:24:52.950 line:80%
Kill the bastard officials!

00:24:54.960 --> 00:24:56.560 line:80%
Kill the bastard officials!

00:25:01.200 --> 00:25:02.040 line:80%
Attack!

00:25:12.520 --> 00:25:13.780 line:80%
Protect His Lordship!

00:25:37.280 --> 00:25:37.870 line:80%
Hyah!

00:25:39.480 --> 00:25:40.070 line:80%
Hyah!

00:25:47.040 --> 00:25:47.590 line:80%
Whoa!

00:25:47.720 --> 00:25:48.390 line:80%
Stop!

00:25:48.760 --> 00:25:50.890 line:80%
My master sent me to deliver a message.

00:25:50.960 --> 00:25:52.870 line:80%
A small unit of the Chongzhou rebel army
has set up an ambush

00:25:52.870 --> 00:25:54.910 line:80%
in the Southern Mountain's woods
in Lin'an.

00:25:54.910 --> 00:25:56.390 line:80%
My Lord, you must go and stop them

00:25:56.390 --> 00:25:58.830 line:80%
to ensure the safety
of the people in Lin'an.

00:25:58.830 --> 00:26:00.240 line:80%
Who is your master?

00:26:01.040 --> 00:26:03.020 line:80%
My master's surname is Xie.

00:26:05.390 --> 00:26:06.480 line:80%
Generals!

00:26:07.240 --> 00:26:09.310 line:80%
To protect the peace of Lin'an's people,

00:26:09.310 --> 00:26:10.810 line:80%
fight alongside me today

00:26:10.910 --> 00:26:12.040 line:80%
and repel the enemy!

00:26:12.390 --> 00:26:13.200 line:80%
Kill!

00:26:13.200 --> 00:26:14.680 line:80%
Kill!

00:26:30.060 --> 00:26:31.630 line:80%
The game is over.

00:26:32.680 --> 00:26:34.350 line:80%
You think bringing me here

00:26:35.240 --> 00:26:36.800 line:80%
can stop all this?

00:26:37.280 --> 00:26:38.410 line:80%
Even if I can't stop it,

00:26:38.410 --> 00:26:39.640 line:80%
I'll still kill you!

00:26:40.040 --> 00:26:41.240 line:80%
You're asking to die!

00:27:00.280 --> 00:27:01.910 line:80%
I didn't bring my butcher knife,

00:27:01.910 --> 00:27:03.660 line:80%
otherwise you'd see

00:27:03.680 --> 00:27:05.680 line:80%
how we butcher pigs for the New Year.

00:28:04.660 --> 00:28:08.370 line:80%
♪ The world is vast ♪

00:28:05.910 --> 00:28:07.520 line:80%
Wasn't it supposed to be
just a small unit?

00:28:07.520 --> 00:28:09.250 line:80%
Why are there reinforcements?

00:28:10.050 --> 00:28:17.020 line:80%
♪ The storm is rising ♪

00:28:11.150 --> 00:28:12.870 line:80%
We can't let them get through
the snow forest,

00:28:12.870 --> 00:28:14.870 line:80%
or the people of Lin'an will suffer!

00:28:15.070 --> 00:28:16.530 line:80%
We have to hold our ground!

00:28:17.640 --> 00:28:22.970 line:80%
♪ Day and night ♪

00:28:23.470 --> 00:28:26.920 line:80%
♪ We strive to save the world ♪

00:28:30.560 --> 00:28:34.920 line:80%
♪ All people ♪

00:28:36.200 --> 00:28:41.610 line:80%
♪ Are part of the past ♪

00:28:39.030 --> 00:28:39.630 line:80%
Hya!

00:28:40.040 --> 00:28:40.870 line:80%
Whoa!

00:28:41.110 --> 00:28:41.830 line:80%
Whoa!

00:28:43.520 --> 00:28:44.370 line:80%
Master?

00:28:43.860 --> 00:28:48.640 line:80%
♪ What's the date today? ♪

00:28:45.480 --> 00:28:47.840 line:80%
Seize all troops who are not

00:28:47.870 --> 00:28:49.330 line:80%
from the Jizhou Army!

00:28:49.160 --> 00:28:55.870 line:80%
♪ How lamentable ♪

00:29:00.290 --> 00:29:01.420 line:80%
General, retreat!

00:29:01.480 --> 00:29:04.110 line:80%
He Jingyuan's Jizhou Army
is coming from the northeast!

00:29:04.110 --> 00:29:05.720 line:80%
The 1000 men we had in ambush

00:29:05.720 --> 00:29:07.520 line:80%
have been completely wiped out!

00:29:07.820 --> 00:29:09.680 line:80%
He Jingyuan arrived so quickly?

00:29:09.830 --> 00:29:11.110 line:80%
You can't run!

00:29:11.130 --> 00:29:11.970 line:80%
Seize him!

00:29:13.870 --> 00:29:15.280 line:80%
General, don't go!

00:29:32.960 --> 00:29:33.980 line:80%
Get him!

00:29:37.910 --> 00:29:39.180 line:80%
I've changed my mind.

00:29:39.750 --> 00:29:42.230 line:80%
Come back with me and be my concubine.

00:30:09.680 --> 00:30:12.280 line:80%
I'm going after him.
Meet me at the usual place.

00:30:26.420 --> 00:30:27.350 line:80%
The usual place?

00:30:28.810 --> 00:30:30.210 line:80%
Where is the usual place?

00:30:31.970 --> 00:30:34.940 line:80%
[Qingping]

00:30:38.480 --> 00:30:38.930 line:80%
Hyah!

00:30:44.040 --> 00:30:44.800 line:80%
My Lord.

00:30:44.800 --> 00:30:45.630 line:80%
My Lord.

00:30:46.070 --> 00:30:47.110 line:80%
My Lord.

00:30:47.440 --> 00:30:49.110 line:80%
Please uphold justice for us!

00:30:49.110 --> 00:30:50.240 line:80%
Have mercy, My Lord!

00:30:50.310 --> 00:30:53.630 line:80%
We were truly forced into a corner.

00:30:53.720 --> 00:30:55.440 line:80%
Folks! Folks!

00:30:55.550 --> 00:30:58.390 line:80%
Take your grain and go home now.

00:30:58.520 --> 00:31:01.390 line:80%
There is more to the grain requisition
than meets the eye.

00:31:01.390 --> 00:31:02.590 line:80%
As for the incident in Ma Village,

00:31:02.590 --> 00:31:05.000 line:80%
the Imperial Court
will investigate thoroughly

00:31:05.000 --> 00:31:08.240 line:80%
and give you all a satisfactory answer.

00:31:08.240 --> 00:31:11.310 line:80%
-Thank you, My Lord!
-Thank you, My Lord!

00:31:14.310 --> 00:31:15.200 line:80%
Don't rush.

00:31:15.390 --> 00:31:16.760 line:80%
Line up and state your names.

00:31:16.760 --> 00:31:17.070 line:80%
Everyone will get theirs.

00:31:17.070 --> 00:31:18.650 line:80%
I got my grain back!

00:31:18.720 --> 00:31:21.050 line:80%
Don't push. There's enough for everyone.

00:31:23.440 --> 00:31:24.350 line:80%
My name.

00:31:24.350 --> 00:31:24.960 line:80%
Okay.

00:31:25.480 --> 00:31:26.070 line:80%
Next.

00:31:33.280 --> 00:31:34.680 line:80%
Lord He!

00:31:36.190 --> 00:31:37.670 line:80%
Lord He!

00:31:38.480 --> 00:31:40.000 line:80%
Thank God you arrived.

00:31:40.150 --> 00:31:41.000 line:80%
Otherwise,

00:31:41.040 --> 00:31:44.480 line:80%
even if I had sacrificed my life
on these city walls,

00:31:44.630 --> 00:31:47.070 line:80%
I wouldn't have stopped these rebels!

00:31:49.520 --> 00:31:50.350 line:80%
Today,

00:31:50.520 --> 00:31:53.440 line:80%
thanks to your contribution,
the people of Lin'an

00:31:54.520 --> 00:31:56.680 line:80%
were spared from disaster.

00:31:57.350 --> 00:31:59.390 line:80%
I feel ashamed.

00:31:59.800 --> 00:32:01.390 line:80%
The military's grain requisition

00:32:01.390 --> 00:32:03.000 line:80%
incited the locals to rebel.

00:32:03.040 --> 00:32:05.830 line:80%
Fortunately, I saw through their scheme

00:32:06.000 --> 00:32:07.680 line:80%
and sent some constables

00:32:07.720 --> 00:32:10.390 line:80%
to block the city gate,

00:32:10.520 --> 00:32:12.810 line:80%
preventing them from entering.

00:32:13.000 --> 00:32:15.200 line:80%
I also overstepped my authority

00:32:15.200 --> 00:32:17.590 line:80%
and seized the officers
in charge of the grain requisition

00:32:17.590 --> 00:32:19.240 line:80%
to appease the public anger.

00:32:19.350 --> 00:32:21.680 line:80%
It's fortunate you arrived in time,

00:32:21.680 --> 00:32:24.680 line:80%
or it would have been a disaster.

00:32:26.040 --> 00:32:27.720 line:80%
Look. Constable Wang...

00:32:28.110 --> 00:32:30.550 line:80%
performed well under my command.

00:32:30.550 --> 00:32:32.830 line:80%
He should be heavily rewarded.

00:32:32.960 --> 00:32:34.040 line:80%
It was my duty.

00:32:35.280 --> 00:32:37.210 line:80%
If you truly wish to grant a reward,

00:32:37.240 --> 00:32:39.590 line:80%
please give the casualties
among the police runners

00:32:39.590 --> 00:32:41.110 line:80%
some extra compensation.

00:32:42.150 --> 00:32:43.590 line:80%
In that case,

00:32:44.680 --> 00:32:48.310 line:80%
everyone who kept the rioters
outside the gate

00:32:48.590 --> 00:32:50.830 line:80%
shall be rewarded.

00:32:51.070 --> 00:32:52.280 line:80%
Thank you, My Lord!

00:32:52.310 --> 00:32:53.520 line:80%
Thank you, My Lord.

00:32:53.680 --> 00:32:54.350 line:80%
My Lord.

00:32:54.760 --> 00:32:57.000 line:80%
There is one more person
who deserves a heavy reward.

00:32:57.000 --> 00:32:57.720 line:80%
Who?

00:33:01.480 --> 00:33:02.540 line:80%
Where's that girl?

00:33:04.040 --> 00:33:04.680 line:80%
My Lord,

00:33:04.720 --> 00:33:07.630 line:80%
the girl he mentioned
is just a servant of mine.

00:33:08.040 --> 00:33:10.520 line:80%
Of course, she should be rewarded too.

00:33:11.520 --> 00:33:13.680 line:80%
Earlier, I saw someone

00:33:13.680 --> 00:33:16.070 line:80%
wearing a green ghost mask
on the city wall.

00:33:16.070 --> 00:33:17.680 line:80%
Who was that?

00:33:24.280 --> 00:33:25.720 line:80%
Are you crazy?

00:33:26.000 --> 00:33:27.390 line:80%
Why won't you let me go?

00:33:27.790 --> 00:33:29.190 line:80%
How did I offend you?

00:33:30.520 --> 00:33:31.780 line:80%
Put down the crossbow,

00:33:32.070 --> 00:33:33.470 line:80%
and I'll spare your life.

00:33:34.390 --> 00:33:35.350 line:80%
Who are you?

00:33:35.910 --> 00:33:37.800 line:80%
What is your relationship with that maid?

00:33:37.800 --> 00:33:40.600 line:80%
Surely you're not afraid
to give your name, right?

00:33:42.870 --> 00:33:44.670 line:80%
Heir Apparent of Lord Changxin,

00:33:45.310 --> 00:33:46.590 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing.

00:34:15.390 --> 00:34:16.640 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an?

00:34:17.830 --> 00:34:18.990 line:80%
You didn't die?

00:34:28.470 --> 00:34:31.120 line:80%
What is your relationship
with that maid on the city wall?

00:34:31.120 --> 00:34:32.870 line:80%
Her skin is so fair.

00:34:33.800 --> 00:34:35.870 line:80%
Kissing her

00:34:36.280 --> 00:34:37.510 line:80%
felt so sweet.

00:35:19.200 --> 00:35:19.870 line:80%
Stop!

00:35:26.510 --> 00:35:27.510 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an?

00:35:43.050 --> 00:35:44.380 line:80%
It's been so many years,

00:35:44.560 --> 00:35:46.960 line:80%
but your martial art
hasn't improved a bit.

00:35:47.050 --> 00:35:48.920 line:80%
You never said

00:35:49.160 --> 00:35:51.430 line:80%
they were 1,000 elite troops
from Chongzhou.

00:35:51.430 --> 00:35:53.510 line:80%
I led barely 100 cavalry,

00:35:53.950 --> 00:35:54.910 line:80%
and even outnumbered ten to one,

00:35:54.910 --> 00:35:56.030 line:80%
I wasn't defeated.

00:35:56.030 --> 00:35:59.310 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an,
your Blood-Robed Cavalry is just so-so.

00:35:59.560 --> 00:36:01.240 line:80%
If you were truly capable,

00:36:01.280 --> 00:36:02.310 line:80%
even without any info,

00:36:02.310 --> 00:36:03.970 line:80%
you wouldn't be in such a mess.

00:36:04.470 --> 00:36:05.640 line:80%
As a commandant,

00:36:05.950 --> 00:36:07.240 line:80%
you ignored strategy

00:36:07.240 --> 00:36:09.100 line:80%
and just charged straight ahead.

00:36:09.280 --> 00:36:11.280 line:80%
I'll remember this today.

00:36:11.510 --> 00:36:12.870 line:80%
Once I recover,

00:36:13.240 --> 00:36:14.910 line:80%
I'll face you in battle again,

00:36:15.240 --> 00:36:17.700 line:80%
and I'll show you
what it means to be in a mess.

00:36:20.280 --> 00:36:21.510 line:80%
I'll wait and see.

00:36:27.280 --> 00:36:29.740 line:80%
Why are they suddenly getting along
so well?

00:36:29.950 --> 00:36:32.720 line:80%
Who was the one who pretended
to be an envoy of the Wei faction,

00:36:32.720 --> 00:36:35.800 line:80%
forged the grain requisition,
and nearly caused a civilian uprising?

00:36:35.800 --> 00:36:36.800 line:80%
Was he caught?

00:36:36.870 --> 00:36:39.670 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing,
the heir apparent of Lord Changxin.

00:36:42.470 --> 00:36:43.910 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing?

00:36:44.560 --> 00:36:46.990 line:80%
He truly is as audacious
as the rumors say.

00:36:51.200 --> 00:36:53.560 line:80%
Your Lordship, if you wish to stabilize
the situation in the Northwest,

00:36:53.560 --> 00:36:55.890 line:80%
you will definitely need me in the future.

00:36:55.910 --> 00:36:57.910 line:80%
-How about we…
-I've always done as I please.

00:36:57.910 --> 00:36:59.160 line:80%
Lord Li, I appreciate

00:36:59.240 --> 00:37:00.120 line:80%
your kindness.

00:37:04.030 --> 00:37:05.910 line:80%
Tang Peiyi said that this strike

00:37:06.160 --> 00:37:08.200 line:80%
was planned long ago by you and my teacher

00:37:08.200 --> 00:37:09.600 line:80%
to ambush enemy supplies

00:37:09.910 --> 00:37:13.120 line:80%
and seize 200,000 piculs
of grain for the frontlines.

00:37:15.160 --> 00:37:16.890 line:80%
Since you can trust my teacher,

00:37:17.460 --> 00:37:18.930 line:80%
why can't you trust me?

00:37:27.080 --> 00:37:28.760 line:80%
Don't you know why, Lord Li?

00:37:29.570 --> 00:37:30.640 line:80%
Are you worried

00:37:30.640 --> 00:37:33.700 line:80%
I was sent by my grandfather
to subvert the Wei faction?

00:37:34.430 --> 00:37:36.390 line:80%
My grandfather is at the Imperial Court,

00:37:36.390 --> 00:37:37.640 line:80%
where the situation is complicated.

00:37:37.640 --> 00:37:41.040 line:80%
It's inevitable to have disagreements
with the Wei faction.

00:37:41.280 --> 00:37:42.990 line:80%
But I have my own pursuit,

00:37:44.680 --> 00:37:46.310 line:80%
which is peace for the land

00:37:46.800 --> 00:37:48.910 line:80%
and freedom from war for the people.

00:37:49.310 --> 00:37:50.560 line:80%
In the past,

00:37:50.720 --> 00:37:52.350 line:80%
the Li family seemed to me

00:37:52.560 --> 00:37:54.560 line:80%
just a bunch of petty opportunists.

00:37:54.830 --> 00:37:56.240 line:80%
After this battle,

00:37:56.680 --> 00:37:58.480 line:80%
I've come to realize something.

00:37:58.990 --> 00:38:02.120 line:80%
You shouldn't be a Li.

00:38:05.310 --> 00:38:07.240 line:80%
I'll take that

00:38:07.560 --> 00:38:09.030 line:80%
as a compliment for now.

00:38:11.560 --> 00:38:14.800 line:80%
Do you plan to return to
the Yanzhou Military Camp immediately?

00:38:14.800 --> 00:38:17.160 line:80%
I will stay in Lucheng with my teacher

00:38:17.560 --> 00:38:20.020 line:80%
to fight to the death
against Lord Changxin.

00:38:26.160 --> 00:38:27.080 line:80%
What about you?

00:38:28.720 --> 00:38:30.120 line:80%
I have my own plans.

00:38:32.830 --> 00:38:35.560 line:80%
When you figure out
what your surname should really be,

00:38:35.560 --> 00:38:37.510 line:80%
come to me to discuss cooperation.

00:38:41.310 --> 00:38:42.510 line:80%
About Mrs. Fan,

00:38:43.280 --> 00:38:44.640 line:80%
what are your plans?

00:38:46.800 --> 00:38:48.360 line:80%
Marrying into the Fan family might be

00:38:48.360 --> 00:38:49.820 line:80%
only a compromise for you,

00:38:50.760 --> 00:38:51.870 line:80%
but for Mrs. Fan,

00:38:51.900 --> 00:38:53.960 line:80%
it means her sincerity is misplaced.

00:38:54.030 --> 00:38:55.570 line:80%
That's too cruel.

00:38:56.760 --> 00:38:58.160 line:80%
This is my family matter.

00:38:58.680 --> 00:39:00.590 line:80%
You don't need to worry about it.

00:39:09.390 --> 00:39:09.950 line:80%
Hya!

00:39:11.560 --> 00:39:12.120 line:80%
Hya!

00:39:50.720 --> 00:39:51.920 line:80%
What took you so long?

00:39:53.390 --> 00:39:54.600 line:80%
Are you hurt?

00:40:02.830 --> 00:40:03.760 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:40:05.730 --> 00:40:07.590 line:80%
That villain fell into the river.

00:40:08.350 --> 00:40:10.030 line:80%
I chased him
for over 10 miles along the road.

00:40:10.030 --> 00:40:11.560 line:80%
That is why I came back late.

00:40:12.760 --> 00:40:13.560 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:40:28.870 --> 00:40:30.870 line:80%
People say that villains live long.

00:40:31.280 --> 00:40:34.940 line:80%
That bastard won't survive
after falling into the river, will he?

00:40:35.680 --> 00:40:36.940 line:80%
He is definitely dead.

00:40:39.030 --> 00:40:42.210 line:80%
What is your relationship
with that maid on the city wall?

00:40:42.210 --> 00:40:44.380 line:80%
Her skin is so fair.

00:40:44.670 --> 00:40:46.440 line:80%
Kissing her

00:40:47.290 --> 00:40:49.040 line:80%
felt so sweet.

00:40:59.800 --> 00:41:00.600 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:41:02.470 --> 00:41:03.200 line:80%
Nothing.

00:41:03.800 --> 00:41:04.720 line:80%
Let me tell you,

00:41:04.720 --> 00:41:06.390 line:80%
when I went to catch the magistrate,

00:41:06.390 --> 00:41:08.120 line:80%
I ran into that bastard.

00:41:08.280 --> 00:41:10.280 line:80%
I didn't expect him to be so skilled.

00:41:11.080 --> 00:41:13.080 line:80%
The shock injured the web of my hand.

00:41:22.830 --> 00:41:24.690 line:80%
I shouldn't have let you go alone.

00:41:25.510 --> 00:41:26.350 line:80%
It's okay.

00:41:26.720 --> 00:41:28.380 line:80%
I kept him tied up the whole way

00:41:28.720 --> 00:41:30.560 line:80%
and stabbed him a few times.

00:41:30.640 --> 00:41:31.600 line:80%
That counts as revenge.